{"h1a93f41bg0927g4b89g9279g5b358c511094": ["Well. It seems we're not invited.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291eec75e9"], "ha29f5f68g212ag4f4dgad61gad5ae57c727f": ["All entrances sealed tight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291eec75e9"], "h9b7683fegc807g4b28gac13g0b60934803ad": ["Look at all those vines spread like vices over the grove. A sour harvest in the making.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291eec75e9"], "h013c8a57g7108g4cddgb9d3g543cb17bd0e9": ["Vines everywhere. They did it. They really did it.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291eec75e9"], "he8a45fdfg08bag4d7ag9925gaf0ad3b45ecd": ["Let's not linger - the ritual is complete.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291eec75e9"], "h84fd85cdgaedag4123g9fd2g94c5a5fa1dad": ["|Karlach comment.|", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291eec75e9"], "h7bebf746g0190g4014ga5a8ge857cfd9bd30": ["Just like that. Sealed tight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291eec75e9"], "hfaaca093ge2ebg4256g8608g3b58e13b5d2a": ["_", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291eec75e9"], "h94252005gb893g4ec7ga977g2ec7aa2da2b7": ["They wanted tieflings out. They got their wish.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Lockdown_PAD_Comment.html", "6fa2053b-495e-905b-2a7a-d6291ee